《玩具熊的五夜后宫：姊妹地点篇》的评语大致上都为正面评语。玩家们都称赞游戏里的配音、背景音乐和幽默都达到应有的目的。[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]给予了67.5分的评分<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/193919-five-nights-at-freddys-sister-location/index.html|title=Five Nights at Freddy's: Sister Location for PC|accessdate=2018-01-06|author=|date=|work=[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]|publisher=|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928173129/http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/193919-five-nights-at-freddys-sister-location/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]也给了10分满6分的评价<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.destructoid.com/review-five-nights-at-freddy-s-sister-location-392230.phtml|title=Review: Five Nights at Freddy's: Sister Location|author=|date=|work=|newspaper=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|accessdate=2018-01-06|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209091814/https://www.destructoid.com/review-five-nights-at-freddy-s-sister-location-392230.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，GameCrate则是给予了10分满7.5分的不错评语。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamecrate.com/reviews/review-sister-location-isnt-fnafbut-it-terrifying/14736|title=Review: Sister Location isn't FNAF...but it is terrifying|accessdate=2018-01-06|author=|date=|work=GameCrate|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929002247/https://www.gamecrate.com/reviews/review-sister-location-isnt-fnafbut-it-terrifying/14736|dead-url=yes}}</ref>The All State网站的鉴定家之Shelby Watson给了这款游戏正面的评价，称赞这个游戏的品质比得上第一作，但不像第一作，这次游戏不允许玩家单靠肌肉和记忆处理玩法。她表示：“每一晚都很不一样，想要像老习惯一样放松游玩根本不可能。游戏变得很多，你被强迫适应并一直保持在座位边缘，等待即将来临的事物。”

